<div><div><h2>OPEC will work to stabilise markets at next meeting: Iraqi deputy minister</h2></div><div>"iraqi deputy oil minister fayadh al-nema said on wednesday that opec will work to stabilise oil markets crude prices and supplies at its next meeting."opec and non-opec producers will work together to restore balance to oil prices and supplies to make sure prices stay stable" he told journalists at an oil exploration conference in baghdad."</div></div>